query: What are the linearity metrics for different segments?
sql:
SELECT
    lm.segment_id, lm.linearity_score, fm.funnel_stage, m.metric_name, q.upside_value
FROM cisco_stage_app.linearity_metrics AS lm
    INNER
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.funnel_metrics AS fm
    ON lm.segment_id = fm.segment_id
    INNER
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.metrics AS m
    ON lm.metric_id = m.metric_id
    LEFT
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.qtd_commit_upside AS q
    ON lm.segment_id = q.segment_id
